{"type": "article", "id": 45158, "title": "有了这六个印章，你可以造出自己的中文字｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-09-13T23:17:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 44046, "name": "来字哪里"}, {"id": 44047, "name": "MOLUK"}, {"id": 38653, "name": "bande"}, {"id": 27564, "name": "Peleg Design"}, {"id": 40440, "name": "Design Bridge"}, {"id": 44048, "name": "Rob Bailey"}, {"id": 44049, "name": "柴田大平"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 185, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170913190524ybqmFVxMwrv3tdAO.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><h3>组字印章 by 来字哪里</h3><p>想设计一套特殊的字体，但因为专业软件设立的门槛望而却步？接触字体设计课之后，台湾设计师王介盈和王蔓霖决定制作一款产品，用更便利的方式推广中文字的魅力。她们将文字解构为六种笔刷，并将它们制作成一套组字印章。这样一来，文字就突破了笔画限制，只要稍许改变方向就能创造出新字——即使是同一个字，也能变化出各种不同的造型。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/laizinali\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价从新台币 888 元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190613lSuR6AhqbXIK8Ctd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190613Pdl2GbDWNcvfFVR9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190613BaNc3wFbjHSq6soP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190614qZfjhp7kX1Ax05vW.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190614fUW9xNVvcDPBgZEy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562972\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pluï by MOLUK</h3><p>瑞士玩具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.moluk.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MOLUK</a> 由设计师 Alex Hochstrasser 和他的建筑师姐姐 Doris 成立于 2011 年，他们的设计宗旨是打造寓教于乐且中性的玩具，让男孩女孩们可以玩在一起。为了让洗澡变得更有趣，他们带来了这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.moluk.com/plui.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pluï</a> 的云朵状玩具球，让小朋友们有机会“造雨”：用手按住上方的小孔不让空气进入“云朵”，内部的水也就不会流出，一旦移开，水就会从下方的小孔排出，像是在下雨一样。和封闭式的橡皮鸭子不同，云朵还能拆开，便于清洗。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190629OCRGeFxuMqNiIfQ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190628Nx8VQ3DHpLvgqljn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.856818\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190628esx3UKINEMyqV6pc.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190628Gk53IEMcendF7PLs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.911364\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Mask Roll Sticker by bande</h3><p>凭借着一片片可以拆开、像贴纸一样的胶带设计，日本和纸胶带品牌 <a href=\"https://bande.ne.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">bande</a> 的 Mask Roll Sticker 系列经常引发抢购热潮。趁着秋季的到来，除了推出类似樱花花瓣的红叶版（目前已在官网售罄）之外，bande 还推出了几款以日本传统色和花纹为主题的款式，比如为人熟知的松竹梅、龟甲纹、千鸟纹以及象征海洋的青海波和它的歌舞伎妆版本。你可以通过<a href=\"https://bande.ne.jp/?mode=grp&amp;gid=1545406\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买，售价从 432 日元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190646nPuNebYLzfEGVRd6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.522895\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190646Ck6pE8iPRWVQn1hS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.522895\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190647kPqDtL9jn2ZgfH8X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.522895\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190646gSR2O4LldZuQ79mf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.522895\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190647Lkxq7ANgReYmt8l6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.522895\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Zesty by Peleg Design</h3><p>在烹饪或是调酒的过程中，有时会需要用上水果调味，为此以色列设计师 Ohad Chiya 为 <a href=\"https://www.peleg-design.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Peleg Design</a> 带来了这个名为 Zesty 的小帮手。这只小变色龙的嘴巴可以切出细细的橙皮，头部的另一侧还能用来给水果去皮。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.peleg-design.com/shop/zesty.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">预定链接</a>，售价为 8 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190929jmIDZGxfk62YFtH4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190928O2sjEZpHPJ4f53Db.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190928NldjPMxFAwDS2yvr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190928UBqC7hYoE2mNfgTp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Choose Love by Design Bridge &amp; Rob Bailey</h3><p>继去年为著名伏特加品牌皇冠（Smirnoff）设计支持 LGBTQ 平权的限定版包装 <a href=\"http://www.designbridge.com/story-behind-love-wins-limited-edition-smirnoff-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Love Wins</a> 之后，英国广告公司 Design Bridge 又在今年的英国骄傲游行（British Pride）期间，为其打造了一个全新的 campaign。今年 Choose Love 主题瓶身并没有延续 Love Wins “一个瓶子一对情侣”的设定，而是精选了由插画师 <a href=\"https://robbailey.studio/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rob Bailey</a> 绘制的六对情侣，希望用取向和身份的多元性为平等的爱发声。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190711V87qyArDJlPjEIb0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190712TqvpbMIE70kh4NuL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.680233\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190711ed40asWRS3U6vYD1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679070\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190712CoI3p7B4RxgXrdFe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190712dUqNs8b50wLmMjIZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">2016 年的 Love Wins，限量 500 瓶，每支瓶子上的情侣都不一样</figcaption></figure></div><h3>Unendurable Line by 柴田大平</h3><p>花 30 秒看别人缓慢地开关电灯可以说是相当无聊的消遣方式了——假如在画面旁边配上实时记录动作的图表，情况或许会不太一样。最近，经常为 NHK 等电视台创作科普动画的日本艺术家<a href=\"https://daiheishibata.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">柴田大平</a>带来了一个名为 Unendurable Line 的动画，将生活中常见动作中的起伏转化为曲线，并为它们设置了一条红色的直线代表阈值。为了营造出戏剧效果，他还配上了来自 <a href=\"http://exnovochamberchoir.com/http___exnovochamberchoir.com/ekusunovu~o_shi_nei_he_chang_tuan.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">EX NOVO</a> 室内合唱团的音乐。你可以通过柴田的 <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/231498722\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vimeo</a> 主页看到完整视频。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190554NSqnMwR8LPIu3WFQ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.490625\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190554dcUr9XeuRsB6yD8n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563077\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190554zgmoyj28csqnCSME.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563077\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170913190554wnKXu4fkZxNpi29O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563077\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}